channel.title: Need help getting my 525 server online
channel.description:
I've gone through all the no-ip, DUC, and port forwarding stuff.
But I need to know how to put in online. I've been through some of the client.java and gui.java files and changed the 127.0.0.1 to the IP I used for the no ip. (spiral-scape.no-ip.org) except where the 127.0.0.1 end with a /cache.
Non of my friends can get on my server. they get an error connecting to the server.
Can someone please sort it out over team viewer? Once you connect I'll open up a note pad and tell you in more detail.
If you can get it to work I'll give you mod on my server (if you want).
I'll send you my team viewer ID and PASS in a private message once you respond to this thread.
